ApiRequestHandler.description:
Contains additional information to be added to the API requests.

Example:
```
 {
    headers: {
        "Authorization": "Basic some-bas64-string",
        "X-API-INSTANCE-NAME": "some api instance name"
    }
 }
```

ICommandVariableTemplate.description:
Defines dynamic variables to be used for run. The key is name of the variable and value is variable template item.
Example:
```
{
    "SOURCE_DATABASE": {
        "value": null,
        "pathToConfiguration": "source.database"
     },
     "SOURCE_SCHEMA": {
         "value": null,
         "pathToConfiguration": ["source", "schema"]
     }
}
```
